{
  "3208930": {
    "name": "갈바테인 : 모험가 길드 사무소",
    "steam_appid": 3208930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「加尔巴泰:冒险者公会事务所」是一款正统奇幻题材的模拟游戏，玩家将扮演公会的接待员，审核冒险者提交的任务是否完成。  游戏采用单元剧（Omnibus）形式展开，每个章节都讲述着发生在奇幻世界中的一段段独立事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TGS 2025</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为纪念参加东京电玩展，已公开更新后的试玩版！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/164fe754ba5f8361995f668e274d4d7f.avif?t=1772178964\" width=1080 height=844 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >审核任务完成情况</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清晨来临，公会接待员的一天也随之开始。需要仔细比对各种线索，判断冒险者是否确实完成了任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/8fc24247c56dfafa5fb7cf9ab3167a33.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/8fc24247c56dfafa5fb7cf9ab3167a33.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/8fc24247c56dfafa5fb7cf9ab3167a33.mp4?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >毕竟，一般人并不了解魔物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大多数委托人对魔物的了解少之又少。因此，接待员需要根据任务描述中的信息来推测目标。之后，还要结合战利品、魔物图鉴、地图、许可证等多种资料，来判断冒险者是否真正完成了任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/30eab98059d151f90c7f0e228cd0dde2.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/30eab98059d151f90c7f0e228cd0dde2.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与冒险者的互动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了做出准确的判断，接待员可以向冒险者提问。关于战利品、关于魔物、甚至是关于失踪的某个人。除此之外，也可以闲聊几句，听听他们的生活故事，或是关于尤斯塔斯大陆的种种传闻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/9289d3e83a5c3d88de27ac4495a43c06.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/9289d3e83a5c3d88de27ac4495a43c06.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/9289d3e83a5c3d88de27ac4495a43c06.mp4?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择，永远掌握在你手中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若你恪守原则，认真履行接待员的职责，公会的声誉必将如日中天。可若是有冒险者带着无法拒绝的理由前来呢？或者你发现了自己梦寐以求的战利品呢？选择的权利始终属于你。只不过……在公会声誉还未跌落谷底之前哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/b33603025efc458be60ffd41826ba4d7.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/b33603025efc458be60ffd41826ba4d7.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/b33603025efc458be60ffd41826ba4d7.mp4?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >公会酒馆的夜晚</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临，公会酒馆也随之开张。  前来消除疲惫的冒险者们，带来了各式各样的故事。  从日常的点滴，到惊心动魄的冒险旅程——甚至可能还有令人心动的爱情传说。  使用魔物的战利品烹饪出「魔物料理」，一边享受美食，一边聆听他们的故事吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔物料理可不是闹着玩的！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用魔物的战利品做菜，可不是一件轻松的事。太黏腻、太刺激，稍不注意还有中毒的危险！因此必须准确掌握其特性，选择合适的烹饪方式。要用能够中和缺点的辅材、恰到好处的香料，甚至还要考虑料理本身的属性。是不是听起来很难？别担心。魔法锅「卡乌先生」（其实是主厨）会帮你一臂之力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/ba0efbda8d58012d908915f8bb3ce981.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/ba0efbda8d58012d908915f8bb3ce981.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/ba0efbda8d58012d908915f8bb3ce981.mp4?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险者的渴望与挣扎</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有的精灵因无法使用魔力，被迫离开了世界树之森；有的矮人虽然是铁匠，却因畏惧火焰而踏上了冒险者之路。每位冒险者都背负着属于自己的创伤与痛苦。这是关于那些只想过平凡日子的人们，他们心中渴望与超越困境的故事。你愿意一同聆听吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/12bc269abe6ca70f38092b576de2d8ad.poster.avif?t=1772178964\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/12bc269abe6ca70f38092b576de2d8ad.webm?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208930/extras/12bc269abe6ca70f38092b576de2d8ad.mp4?t=1772178964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
